  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Saturday 19 January 2008" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Saturday 19 January 2008" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="Lead Level Designer, Gothenburg" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Lead Level Designer, Gothenburg" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p>GRIN is looking for an experienced Lead Level Designer for the Gothenburg Studio to work for a major title on the next Gen Platforms and PC.<strong><br />
<br />
Responsibilities</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Work on site at the Grin Studio in Gothenburg and manage the level</li>
    <li>design team by providing them with creative direction, guidance,</li>
    <li>instructions and schedules.</li>
    <li>Meet project deadlines/milestones as set by the project manager</li>
    <li>Meet creative goals as set by the Creative director and Lead</li>
    <li>designer</li>
    <li>Be a key collaborator in setting up the creative-, and</li>
    <li>production-oriented guidelines for the level designers.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />
<strong>Expectations</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Extensive singleplayer level design experience.</li>
    <li>Deep understanding of gameplay from a level design perspective.</li>
    <li>Experience of planning and creating production schedules.</li>
    <li>Good communicator both verbally and in written form.</li>
    <li>Must be able to take direction from the creative leads.</li>
</ul>
<p><br />
If you are interested in the position, send a cover letter and CV via our web form or e-mail.</p></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#106;&#111;&#98;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
      </div>
